# Club "book of record" member data (roster incl. minors' full birthdates,
# gender, OEFOL-IDs, and members with no public results) - the private
# source of truth for the member-identity mapping. NEVER committed or
# published: only its derived effect (cleaner result grouping + canonical
# display names + birth YEAR, all already public-grade) reaches the public
# DB. See build/build_db.py's member-registry integration.
data/private/
site/data/*.db-journal
